ifully balanced, smooth-sipping IPA for every occasion.','Night-Shift-Santilli-IPA.jpg'),(43,'Night Shift Santilli IPA - 24 Pack','beer',13,8,'The beer pours bright gold with a nose of grapefruit zest and pine needles. Begins with big citrus flavors and a light, malty sweetness. Finishes clean, pleasantly bitter, and crisp. A boldly flavored, beautifully balanced, smooth-sipping IPA for every occasion.','Night-Shift-Santilli-IPA.jpg'),(44,'Stella Artois - 6 Pack','beer',6,2,'Belgium/USA - Euro Pale Ale - 5.0% ABV. Brewed in US, staying true to the time-honored Belgian recipe, Crafted with three ingredients-saazhops, malted barley, and water giving its wonderful hop aroma, well-balanced malt sweetness, crisp hop bitterness and a soft dry finish.','Stella-Artois.jpeg'),(45,'Stella Artois - 12 Pack','beer',6,4,'Belgium/USA - Euro Pale Ale - 5.0% ABV. Brewed in US, staying true to the time-honored Belgian recipe, Crafted with three ingredients-saazhops, malted barley, and water giving its wonderful hop aroma, well-balanced malt sweetness, crisp hop bitterness and a soft dry finish.','Stella-Artois.jpeg'),(46,'Stella Artois - 24 Pack','beer',6,8,'Belgium/USA - Euro Pale Ale - 5.0% ABV. Brewed in US, staying true to the time-honored Belgian recipe, Crafted with three ingredients-saazhops, malted barley, and water giving its wonderful hop aroma, well-balanced malt sweetness, crisp hop bitterness and a soft dry finish.','Stella-Artois.jpeg'),(47,'AutoCAD 2022','book',16,1,'AutoCAD 2022 Instructor is an ideal reference guide, unlike tutorial-oriented books where specific information is hard to relocate. Because these chapters focus on related commands, and complete coverage for each command is given in one place, the commands, procedures, and applications are easy to reference. Tabbed pages help locate tables, lists, appendices, and the comprehensive index.','autocad.png'),(48,'AutoCAD 2022','book',16,2,'AutoCAD 2022 Instructor is an ideal reference guide, unlike tutorial-oriented books where specific information is hard to relocate. Because these chapters focus on related commands, and complete coverage for each command is given in one place, the commands, procedures, and applications are easy to reference. Tabbed pages help locate tables, lists, appendices, and the comprehensive index.','autocad.png'),(49,'Java Parsing Collection XML JSON','book',17,1,'The complexity of life, because they do not understand to simplify the complex, simple is the beginning of wisdom. From the essence of practice, this book to briefly explain the concept and vividly cultivate programming interest, this book easy and quickly learn Java parse XML JSON and Collections.','javaparsing.png'),(50,'Java Parsing Collection XML JSON','book',17,2,'The complexity of life, because they do not understand to simplify the complex, simple is the beginning of wisdom. From the essence of practice, this book to briefly explain the concept and vividly cultivate programming interest, this book easy and quickly learn Java parse XML JSON and Collections.','javaparsing.png'),(51,'Jump Start CSS','book',18,1,'This short SitePoint book provides readers with a fun and yet practical introduction to Cascading Style Sheets, the language used to style and lay out all web pages. This book will quickly get you up to speed with the fundamentals of CSS and give you the confidence to start experimenting on your own.','jumpstartcss.png'),(52,'Jump Start CSS','book',18,2,'This short SitePoint book provides readers with a fun and yet practical introduction to Cascading Style Sheets, the language used to style and lay out all web pages. This book will quickly get you up to speed with the fundamentals of CSS and give you the confidence to start experimenting on your own.','jumpstartcss.png'),(53,'Learn SQL','book',19,1,'Learn SQL FastConcepts in this book are presented in a to-the-point and concise style to cater to the busy individual. With this book, you can learn SQL in just one day and start coding immediately.SQL for BeginnersComplex topics are broken down into simple steps with clear and carefully chosen examples to ensure that you can easily master SQL even if you have never coded before','sqloneday.png'),(54,'Learn SQL','book',19,2,'Learn SQL FastConcepts in this book are presented in a to-the-point and concise style to cater to the busy individual. With this book, you can learn SQL in just one day and start coding immediately.SQL for BeginnersComplex topics are broken down into simple steps with clear and carefully chosen examples to ensure that you can easily master SQL even if you have never coded before','sqloneday.png'),(55,'Learning Linux binary Analysis','book',20,1,'This book will start by taking you through UNIX/Linux object utilities, and will move on to teaching you all about the ELF specimen. You will learn about process tracing, and will explore the different types of Linux and UNIX viruses, and how you can make use of ELF Virus Technology to deal with them.','linuxbinary.png'),(56,'Learning Linux binary Analysis','book',20,2,'This book will start by taking you through UNIX/Linux object utilities, and will move on to teaching you all about the ELF specimen. You will learn about process tracing, and will explore the different types of Linux and UNIX viruses, and how you can make use of ELF Virus Technology to deal with them.','linuxbinary.png'),(57,'Mastering matplotlib','book',21,1,'Matplotlib is a Python plotting library that provides a large feature set for a multitude of platforms. Given the depth of the library\'s legacy and the variety of related open source projects, gaining expert knowledge can be a time-consuming and often confusing process.','matplotlib.png'),(58,'Mastering matplotlib','book',21,2,'Matplotlib is a Python plotting library that provides a large feature set for a multitude of platforms. Given the depth of the library\'s legacy and the variety of related open source projects, gaining expert knowledge can be a time-consuming and often confusing process.','matplotlib.png'),(59,'Advanced Semiconductor Memories','book',22,1,'A valuable reference for the most vital microelectronic components in the marketplace DRAMs are the technology drivers of high volume semiconductor fabrication processes for new generation products that, in addition to computer markets, are finding increased usage in automotive, aviation, military and space, telecommunications, and wireless industries.','semiconductormemories.png'),(60,'Advanced Semiconductor Memories','book',22,2,'A valuable reference for the most vital microelectronic components in the marketplace DRAMs are the technology drivers of high volume semiconductor fabrication processes for new generation products that, in addition to computer markets, are finding increased usage in automotive, aviation, military and space, telecommunications, and wireless industries.','semiconductormemories.png'),(61,'Data Structures & Algorithm Analysis in Java','book',12,1,'Techniques for representing data are presented within the context of assessing costs and benefits, promoting an understanding of the principles of algorithm analysis and the effects of a chosen physical medium. ','algorithmanalysis.png'),(62,'Data Structures & Algorithm Analysis in Java','book',12,2,'Techniques for representing data are presented within the context of assessing costs and benefits, promoting an understanding of the principles of algorithm analysis and the effects of a chosen physical medium. ','algorithmanalysis.png'),(63,'Full-Stack React, TypeScript, and Node','book',23,1,'React sets the standard for building high-performance client-side web apps. Node.js is a scalable application server that is used in thousands of websites, while GraphQL is becoming the standard way for large websites to provide data and services to their users. Together, these technologies, when reinforced with the capabilities of TypeScript, provide a cutting-edge stack for complete web application development.','typescriptandnode.png'),(64,'Full-Stack React, TypeScript, and Node','book',23,2,'React sets the standard for building high-performance client-side web apps. Node.js is a scalable application server that is used in thousands of websites, while GraphQL is becoming the standard way for large websites to provide data and services to their users. Together, these technologies, when reinforced with the capabilities of TypeScript, provide a cutting-edge stack for complete web application development.','typescriptandnode.png'),(65,'Java Threads','book',24,1,'This book discusses problems like deadlock, race conditions, and starvation in detail, helping you to write code without hidden bugs.Java Threads, Third Edition, has been thoroughly expanded and revised. It incorporates the concurrency utilities from java.util.concurrent throughout. New chapters cover thread performance, using threads with Swing, threads and Collection classes, thread pools, and threads and I/O . Developers who cannot yet deploy J2SE 5.0 can use thread utilities provided in the Appendix to achieve similar functionality with earlier versions of Java.','javathreads.png'),(66,'Java Threads','book',24,2,'This book discusses problems like deadlock, race conditions, and starvation in detail, helping you to write code without hidden bugs.Java Threads, Third Edition, has been thoroughly expanded and revised. It incorporates the concurrency utilities from java.util.concurrent throughout. New chapters cover thread performance, using threads with Swing, threads and Collection classes, thread pools, and threads and I/O . Developers who cannot yet deploy J2SE 5.0 can use thread utilities provided in the Appendix to achieve similar functionality with earlier versions of Java.','javathreads.png'),(67,'JavaScript Async','book',25,1,'Asynchronous programming is essential to the modern web and at last JavaScript programmers have the tools to do the job - the Promise object and the async and await commands. These are so elegant in their design that you need to know about them if only to be impressed. It is likely that other languages will incorporate similar facilities in the future. While async and await make asynchronous code as easy to use as synchronous code there are a lot of subtle things going on and to really master the situation you need to know about Promises and you need to know how the JavaScript dispatch queue works.','javascriptasync.png'),(68,'JavaScript Async','book',25,2,'Asynchronous programming is essential to the modern web and at last JavaScript programmers have the tools to do the job - the Promise object and the async and await commands. These are so elegant in their design that you need to know about them if only to be impressed. It is likely that other languages will incorporate similar facilities in the future. While async and await make asynchronous code as easy to use as synchronous code there are a lot of subtle things going on and to really master the situation you need to know about Promises and you need to know how the JavaScript dispatch queue works.','javascriptasync.png'),(69,'JUnit Pocket Guide','book',26,1,'JUnit, created by Kent Beck and Erich Gamma, is an open source framework for test-driven development in any Java-based code. JUnit automates unit testing and reduces the effort required to frequently test code while developing it.','junit.png'),(70,'JUnit Pocket Guide','book',26,2,'JUnit, created by Kent Beck and Erich Gamma, is an open source framework for test-driven development in any Java-based code. JUnit automates unit testing and reduces the effort required to frequently test code while developing it.','junit.png'),(71,'Maven The Definitive Guide','book',27,1,'For too long, developers have worked on disorganized application projects, where every part seemed to have its own build system, and no common repository existed for information about the state of the project. Now there\'s help. The long-awaited official documentation to Maven is here.','mavenguide.png'),(72,'Maven The Definitive Guide','book',27,2,'For too long, developers have worked on disorganized application projects, where every part seemed to have its own build system, and no common repository existed for information about the state of the project. Now there\'s help. The long-awaited official documentation to Maven is here.','mavenguide.png'),(73,'MongoDB','book',28,1,'This book is a comprehensive guide to MongoDB for application developers. The book begins by explaining what makes MongoDB unique and describing its ideal use cases. A series of chapters designed for MongoDB mastery then leads into detailed examples for leveraging MongoDB in e-commerce, social networking, analytics, and other common applications. Numerous examples will help you develop confidence in the crucial area of data modeling. This is well-organized book which provides proper explanation you\'ll need as a student and enough detail to satisfy a developer. Several examples will help you develop confidence in the crucial area of data modeling. You\'ll also love the deep explanations of each feature, including replication, auto-sharding, and deployment.','mongodb.png'),(74,'MongoDB','book',28,2,'This book is a comprehensive guide to MongoDB for application developers. The book begins by explaining what makes MongoDB unique and describing its ideal use cases. A series of chapters designed for MongoDB mastery then leads into detailed examples for leveraging MongoDB in e-commerce, social networking, analytics, and other common applications. Numerous examples will help you develop confidence in the crucial area of data modeling. This is well-organized book which provides proper explanation you\'ll need as a student and enough detail to satisfy a developer. Several examples will help you develop confidence in the crucial area of data modeling. You\'ll also love the deep explanations of each feature, including replication, auto-sharding, and deployment.','mongodb.png'),(75,'React Design Patterns and Best Practices','book',29,1,'Build high-performing applications by optimizing componentsIn DetailTaking a complete journey through the most valuable design patterns in React, this book demonstrates how to apply design patterns and best practices in real-life situations, whether that\'s for new or already existing projects. It will help you to make your applications more flexible, perform better, and easier to maintain - giving your workflow a huge boost when it comes to speed without reducing quality. ','reactdesign.png'),(76,'React Design Patterns and Best Practices','book',29,2,'Build high-performing applications by optimizing componentsIn DetailTaking a complete journey through the most valuable design patterns in React, this book demonstrates how to apply design patterns and best practices in real-life situations, whether that\'s for new or already existing projects. It will help you to make your applications more flexible, perform better, and easier to maintain - giving your workflow a huge boost when it comes to speed without reducing quality. ','reactdesign.png');
